N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 19 ยง 936.1 - Applicability

State Regulations

This part shall apply to the following individuals: (a) The four statewide elected
officials; (b) State officers or
employees; and
(c) Political party
chairmen; who are required to file an annual statement of financial
disclosure pursuant to section
73-a
of
the Public Officers Law. Notes
